{"id":9724,"date":"2024-01-26T13:36:35","date_gmt":"2020-05-26T08:06:35","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=9724"},"modified":"2021-10-15T12:10:58","modified_gmt":"2021-10-15T06:40:58","slug":"modern-minimalistic-bedroom-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-minimalistic-bedroom-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Bring Serenity Home With These Modern Minimalistic Bedroom Designs"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Minimalist bedroom designs don&#8217;t translate to stark and monotonous spaces. It&#8217;s about scaling back a little to create tranquillising and thoughtful space in your home to unwind. To prove it, we bring you some of our favourite minimalist bedroom designs that will make you fall in love with your bedroom again and again.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you want your bedroom to look and feel like it&#8217;s no short of a resort or hotel? That&#8217;s impossible with clunky interiors, inconsistent decor and loud colour schemes. A clean and clutter-free space becomes an unattainable dream when your bedroom is not designed on the right foundation. Clean lines and a neutral palette define <strong>modern minimalistic style bedrooms<\/strong>. This coupled with stripped-down simplicity that goes hand in hand with designing a comfortable and peaceful bedroom ideal to unwind in.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Nature-Inspired Modern Minimalist Bedroom Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you like the idea of hints of nature in your bedroom but don&#8217;t wish to be overwhelmed by the roughness of it then a minimalist style of interior design should be your approach to keep things exciting. See the antlers on the wall of this stunning minimalistic bedroom design. Although the focal point of this bedroom is the antler on a display wall, a soothing white colour palette brings in a sense of calm and serenity to this bedroom. This bedroom design is clean with limited decor such as a few potted plants on the window sill.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131048\/modern-minimalist-bedroom-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modern minimalist bedroom interior design with a few potted plants on the window sill\" class=\"wp-image-9730\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131048\/modern-minimalist-bedroom-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131048\/modern-minimalist-bedroom-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131048\/modern-minimalist-bedroom-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131048\/modern-minimalist-bedroom-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Fusion Of Rustic And Minimalistic Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In this bedroom, rustic style meets minimalism perfectly. A queen-sized wooden bed and an exposed brick wall bring in a charming countryside feel to this space. An earthy colour palette, wooden accents and snow-white linen add much-needed patterns and textures to this bedroom. If you love old-world rustic style of interiors but still wish to keep your bedroom clutter-free, this one&#8217;s an excellent choice for you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131233\/rustic-and-minimalistic-bedroom-design.jpg\" alt=\"Rustic style minimalistic bedroom design with a queen-sized wooden bed and an exposed brick wall\" class=\"wp-image-9732\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131233\/rustic-and-minimalistic-bedroom-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131233\/rustic-and-minimalistic-bedroom-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131233\/rustic-and-minimalistic-bedroom-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131233\/rustic-and-minimalistic-bedroom-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Modern Minimalist Kids Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If there is one room in any home that is always unorganised and stuffed with unnecessary things lying on the floor it is the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/kids-bedroom-design\/\">kids&#8217; bedroom<\/a>. A minimalist style of interior design in your kids&#8217; bedroom will help you keep this space organised and clutter-free all day long. This bedroom is designed with simplicity in an all white colour scheme, however, the element of fun is intact with the abstract wall art and decor pieces.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131138\/modern-minimalist-kids-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Modern minimalist kids bedroom design with the abstract wall art and decor pieces\" class=\"wp-image-9731\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131138\/modern-minimalist-kids-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131138\/modern-minimalist-kids-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131138\/modern-minimalist-kids-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26131138\/modern-minimalist-kids-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Out Of Sight Out Of Mind<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If there was ever a debate on how much more minimalist can a bedroom be, then this bedroom design would win fair and square! Your space can&#8217;t get any more minimalist than eliminating the bed when not in need. This bedroom design features a Murphy bed that can be pushed back to the wall when not needed leaving behind a clutter-free bedroom with ample floor space to move around. Besides, the soft white colour palette, a sideboard, and just the right amount of lighting on top of the headboard tie this space together. If you live in a small sized apartment or your room is the smallest one in the house, then your search for a minimalistic style bedroom ends here! A space-saving solution like a murphy bed in a minimalist set-up like this one plays well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130953\/minimalistic-style-bedroom-with-murphy-bed.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist bedroom ideas with a murphy bed that can be pushed back to the wall\" class=\"wp-image-9729\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130953\/minimalistic-style-bedroom-with-murphy-bed.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130953\/minimalistic-style-bedroom-with-murphy-bed-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130953\/minimalistic-style-bedroom-with-murphy-bed-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130953\/minimalistic-style-bedroom-with-murphy-bed-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Stairway To Your Dream<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This minimalist bedroom design blends whites and browns for a comforting colour scheme. The one feature that steals the show in this bedroom is the utilisation of available space. A dresser unit is installed right above the bed at the lower level. Both levels are bridged together with a classic wooden stairway. The perfect sized platform bed, compact side tables, and make night time reading a pleasant experience. This design works well in a studio, 1BHK apartment or even a bedroom that\u2019s big enough.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130902\/minimalist-bedroom-design-with-classic-wooden-stairway.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist bedroom design with a classic wooden stairway suitable in a studio and 1bhk apartment\" class=\"wp-image-9728\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130902\/minimalist-bedroom-design-with-classic-wooden-stairway.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130902\/minimalist-bedroom-design-with-classic-wooden-stairway-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130902\/minimalist-bedroom-design-with-classic-wooden-stairway-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130902\/minimalist-bedroom-design-with-classic-wooden-stairway-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Atlantis Is Calling<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Let your bedroom be just as magical and mysterious as the lost city of Atlantis with an alluring colour scheme of blues and whites. This bedroom design features the blue laminated wardrobe with storage, white sheer curtains, and an elegant bed. Artistic wall decor binds this <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom interior design<\/a> to perfection.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130729\/minimalist-bedroom-with-alluring-colour-scheme-blues-whites.jpg\" alt=\"Minimalist bedroom with blue laminated wardrobe with storage, white sheer curtains\" class=\"wp-image-9726\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130729\/minimalist-bedroom-with-alluring-colour-scheme-blues-whites.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130729\/minimalist-bedroom-with-alluring-colour-scheme-blues-whites-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130729\/minimalist-bedroom-with-alluring-colour-scheme-blues-whites-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130729\/minimalist-bedroom-with-alluring-colour-scheme-blues-whites-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5 Simple Tips To Organise Your Bedroom<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now that you know what a modern minimalistic bedroom looks like and have probably picked your favourite one by now, let us give you some easy tips to let your bedroom live up its name. Here is how to keep it organised!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Dont leave your bed messy<\/li><li>Limit the clutter on empty surfaces<\/li><li>Reduce the items on your bedside table<\/li><li>The floor must always be clear<\/li><li>Be particular with additions to your bedroom<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130641\/5-simple-tips-to-organise-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"5 simple tips to organise your bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-9725\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130641\/5-simple-tips-to-organise-bedroom.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130641\/5-simple-tips-to-organise-bedroom-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130641\/5-simple-tips-to-organise-bedroom-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/26130641\/5-simple-tips-to-organise-bedroom-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Also Read:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/minimalistic-living-room\/\">Minimalistic Living Room Design Ideas<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/modern-minimalist-kitchen-designs\/\">Modern Minimalist Kitchen Designs<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modern-bedroom-designs\/\">Modern Bedroom Designs<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"for